questions.quote: Look, you know what? If this is the way you feel, then maybe you should take it.
Okay, swear you won't tell, but when Mark left he gave me a key to Joanna's office. Do you wanna see the list?
You'd better do something, or I'm gonna walk out that door right now! Well? Are you gonna?
Are you kidding me? Watch! Well I can't do it with you guys watching me!
This is crazy. I mean, six years? And because of me you guys aren't gonna be together? Can I ask you something? Really, what is this thing with you and Rachel?
I don't know, you know, just the way she waltzed in here all smart, and tall! You know, and just swept Joey off his feet... I mean, nobody else has a chance!
Nooo!! She's really dull! And she gets this gross mascara goop thing in the corner of her eye!
Alright, lets see if you're as good in person as you are on paper. Make me a salad.
Yeah, yeah, okay. Uh, look buddy, I came with that girl, and I had this plan to kiss her at the new years countdown – I'm trying to win her over, so I was wondering if..
Well I know I was an idiot! And I tried to forget you, I really did! Y'know after we had lunch last year I spent six months in Africa trying to get you out of my head!
